OL,3,EDIGI'S ON OUR WAY TO WEMBLEYG``````````
OL,5,GRespect is due to the Amiga, and in    
OL,6,Gyour heart of hearts you know this to  
OL,7,Gbe true.                               
OL,8,G                                       
OL,9,GSensible Soccer has yet to be surpassed
OL,10,Gby any of the newer flashier           
OL,11,Gconsole/PC games. But in saying that,  
OL,12,Gmost other Amiga games have been.      
OL,13,GHmm... We'll get our coats, shall we?  
OL,15,BMark and Ted, Leicester                
OL,17,FDid one of you hold the pen still while
OL,18,Fthe other one moved the paper?         
