OL,3,EDIGI'S GOING TO DO IT AGAING```````````
OL,5,GAt last that stupid "my machine is     
OL,6,Gbetter than yours" argument has died   
OL,7,Gdown, but there's still no happy       
OL,8,Gending. You still have people writing  
OL,9,Gin saying they have an Amiga which is  
OL,10,Gsomehow still alive and kicking.       
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,GWake up you idiots! Why spend loads of 
OL,13,Gmoney for an upgrade when it would be  
OL,14,Geasier and more enjoyable to get a     
OL,15,Gdecent PC instead, or even a console   
OL,16,Gwith tons of games?BJ Diamond          
OL,17,F                                       
OL,18,FWe've no idea who disturbed the Amiga  
OL,19,Fhornets' nest again. Was it you?       
