OL,3,ETHE BOYS FROM FULHAM, BOYS FROM FULHAMG
OL,4,G                                       
OL,5,GIn reply to Stuart Campbell's "life of 
OL,6,Ga PC owner" saga, I have two points:   
OL,8,E1GPCs are not for people without       
OL,9,GPC-owning friends. You can't get along 
OL,10,Gwithout the help and inspiration of    
OL,11,Gothers when resolving problems, such   
OL,12,Gsoundcards. Is Campbell a loner?       
OL,14,E2GNot all PC owners feel they need to  
OL,15,Gride the cutting edge of technology.   
OL,16,GEverything comes down in price after a 
OL,17,Gwhile.BMark Dennison                   
