OL,3,ETHE BOYS FROM FARM LANEG```````````````
OL,5,GI may have criticised your mag in the  
OL,6,Gpast, saying you couldn't compete with 
OL,7,Gother mags because you don't have      
OL,8,Gscreenshots or demo CDs.               
OL,9,G                                       
OL,10,GHowever, your E3 coverage was excellent
OL,11,Gand you have proved yourself to be     
OL,12,Gbetter than other mags by breaking the 
OL,13,Gnews as it happened. Well done.        
OL,14,G                                       
OL,15,GOne thing. Why don't you have an       
OL,16,Geditorial - editor, staff writer, etc? 
OL,17,BJohn Mearnef, Lancs                    
OL,19,FBecause Digitiser is written by droids.
